{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are a writer who is too lazy to work on his books. Your path will be difficult: endless rejections, small payments, competition with other authors. It's no wonder that your desire to create becomes less and less every day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But perhaps happiness and success await you at the very end?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Get motivated:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/MinigamesENG.gif?t=1734517421\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Writing books empties your motivation scale. Do side activities to fill it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Moreover, each trial requires its own approach to replenish your motivation points. Do you have enough spirit to reach the end?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Write books in your own style:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/BookWritingENG.gif?t=1734517421\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The following genres are available for writing books: </strong> crime novel, detective, horror, fantasy, adventure, sci-fi. Choose the genre of your book and start creating! Atmosphere, protagonist character, setting and much more \u2013 <strong>only you determine what your story will be</strong>!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Wise mentors and true friends:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/FriendsENG.gif?t=1734517421\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each friend has a carefully developed storyline. And you can witness all of them! Take part in the investigation of a series of murders, go on a dangerous foray into a creepy dungeon \u2013 in <strong>Lazy Writer</strong> you can find a story you'll like!